⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Moridin
node WOT · WOT · ⟦Moridin:WOT:be5efc⟧

WHO   — Moridin — Death, the Nae'blis, Ishamael reborn
WHAT  — The final incarnation of Ishamael — named Nae'blis, first among the Shadow's servants, the only one to wield the True Power.
WHERE — WOT · The Wheel of Time  Framework inputs: the Shadow  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — A chance crossing of balefire binds his fate to Rand's, body and soul, to the very end at Shayol Ghul.
HOW   — Given a new body by the Dark One, he draws the True Power directly, its overuse marking his eyes with the black flecks called saa.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Death walks in a new body, and is tired of the long turning.

